TITLE: Adding Initialization Method for Static Initialization
DESCRIPTION: Adds an initialize method to the ModItems class that can be called from the mod's initializer to ensure all static fields are evaluated properly, loading the registered items into the game.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FabricMC/fabric-docs/blob/main/versions/1.21/develop/items/first-item.md#2025-04-05_snippet_2

