SOURCE: https://github.com/FabricMC/fabric-docs/blob/main/versions/1.21/develop/entities/damage-types.md#2025-04-05_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
:::1
public class TaterBlock extends Block {
	public TaterBlock(Settings settings) {
		super(settings);
	}

	@Override
	public void onSteppedOn(World world, BlockPos pos, BlockState state, Entity entity) {
		if (!world.isClient() && entity instanceof LivingEntity) {
			// Create a damage source from our damage type
			DamageSource damageSource = new DamageSource(
				world.getRegistryManager().get(RegistryKeys.DAMAGE_TYPE).entryOf(FabricDocsReferenceDamageTypes.TATER)
			);
			// Deal damage to the entity
			entity.damage(damageSource, 5.0F);
		}

		super.onSteppedOn(world, pos, state, entity);
	}
}
```

