TITLE: Sheep Entity Mixin for Custom Event in Java
DESCRIPTION: Mixin implementation to trigger the custom sheep shear event from the SheepEntity class.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FabricMC/fabric-docs/blob/main/versions/1.20.4/develop/events.md#2025-04-05_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
