TITLE: Merging Codecs into Pair in Java
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to combine two separate Codecs into a Pair Codec and serialize data using it.
SOURCE: https://github.com/FabricMC/fabric-docs/blob/main/develop/codecs.md#2025-04-05_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
// Create two separate boxed codecs
Codec<Integer> firstCodec = Codec.INT.fieldOf("i_am_number").codec();
Codec<Boolean> secondCodec = Codec.BOOL.fieldOf("this_statement_is_false").codec();

// Merge them into a pair codec
